There are a lot of helpers. Use this guide to sort them out:

Global Helpers
============================

Global helpers are available everywhere.

/app/helpers/page

  For displaying lists of pages, creating pages, and linking to pages.

/app/helpers/ui

  For UI display elements: widgets, images, linking, navigation, etc.

/app/helpers/utility

  Global helpers that don't relate to UI elements. For example, time functions,
  caching, etc.

Controller Specific Helpers
============================

/app/helpers

  Only controller specific helpers should go here.

/app/base_page

  Helpers that are used by controllers that are decended from BasePage (ie tools)

/app/me

  For use by controllers in app/controllers/me



